{"about_the_game":"Ever wondered if you could Count Cards? I did too, so I created this game to assist; by providing ALL the data you would need, at runtime.<br><br>Take control of the Game: <i>Pause</i>, <i>Resume</i>, see all <i>Previous Cards</i>, their Card Count Value, the Running &amp; True Count; all in order to '<strong>keep the count</strong>' -providing an advantage to the Player, when to bet <strong>BIGGER!</strong>.<br><br>The game of Blackjack will (generally) consist of various Decks, &amp; knowing the current <i>Running Count</i> will enable you to calculate these better strategic betting points. See Utilities below for more info.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Card Counting Systems;</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>NEW: KO (Knock Out) : Running Count, Only (Unbalanced) Introduced: 31.03.22</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hi-Lo : Running Count &amp; True Count (Balanced)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Blackjack, Play;</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bet ($5, $10, $25, $50 Chips), Split, Double, Stand, Hit, Insurance</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2No. Static BOT's (Adding some difficulty to Player Counting)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Visual Arm Betting Animations (Hit, Stand, Split, Double)</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828070/extras/Betting_Gif1.gif?t=1649184932\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Utilities;</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>How to Card Count Interactive Screen (New Update)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Session(s) Record : With Win/Loss Counts</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Complete Game Card Listing/Viewing [Toggable]</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pause (End of hand) Play [Toggable]</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Music Player</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>True Count Chart (Trendline)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Touch Screen P.C/Settings</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Basic Strategy Chart (Illuminated Play, based on current hand)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Advanced Play's (Deviations) Chart (Illuminated Play, based on current hand)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Card Count Values [Visibility Toggleable]</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Simulator 2100;</h2><br>Run hundreds, if not thousands of Blackjack games;<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>...using Basic Strategy &amp; *Adv. Deviations (*Toggleable)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Set Custom Bet Amounts, Per True Count (-1 to +17)</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Set Custom Deals Per Hour/Hours Played</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Set Custom Starting Funds</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Set Custom Deck Penetrations</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Deck(s);</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose: 1 to 8 decks. (6, as default -as most Casinos).</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customizable;</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Game Mode</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Table Felt</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Arm Interactive Colour</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Card Outline Colour</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Room/Table: Light Controls</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mini-Shop Buy Items (a WIP)</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First BlackJack","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1828070/10678c227bd6811fa63bb82bd5b5ec741ee0e393.jpg"},{"name":"Take The Dealer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1828070/cb7b6792bfda92728a6b7150617a14d9d1f15419.jpg"}],"total":2},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1649184932","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828070/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1649184932","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828070/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1649184932","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828070/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=16491